00:31:29.954 --> 00:31:33.804
work regarding breast cancer. My disclosures.

562
00:31:33.874 --> 00:31:37.864
But a critical challenge that we face when we think about

563
00:31:37.874 --> 00:31:41.164
breast cancer care and treatment is the fact that

