00:31:41.654 --> 00:31:45.114
older and younger patients tend to have worse outcomes.

565
00:31:45.974 --> 00:31:49.864
This is work conducted by our friend and colleague, Rachel Freedman, looking

566
00:31:49.894 --> 00:31:50.944
at SEER data, and

567
00:31:51.914 --> 00:31:55.094
since updated, looking at the adjusted hazard ratio of breast

