00:33:44.054 --> 00:33:47.674
data and data sets that were available to try to answer this question.

599
00:33:47.774 --> 00:33:51.394
So we started with an approach where we took available data sets

600
00:33:52.054 --> 00:33:54.794
and looked at any correlations with age.

