00:34:11.935 --> 00:34:15.495
understanding then is if we just look transcriptomic, what are the

607
00:34:15.534 --> 00:34:17.694
differences? Are there differences with age?

608
00:34:17.975 --> 00:34:21.814
And then we back that work up with tissue-based validation

