00:35:05.394 --> 00:35:09.174
But the bottom line is that this data,

623
00:35:09.234 --> 00:35:13.194
looking at correlations with age and transcriptomic profiles and

624
00:35:13.254 --> 00:35:17.204
CellChat analyses to look at how cells may be interacting with one another

625
00:35:17.234 --> 00:35:20.974
in the microenvironment, focusing on a few cell types here, we were able to

626
00:35:21.014 --> 00:35:23.194
design a landscape of

627
00:35:24.154 --> 00:35:27.494
age-associated estrogen receptor-positive breast cancer,

