00:36:30.574 --> 00:36:33.884
breast cancer, we see a super inflamed phenotype,

646
00:36:34.074 --> 00:36:36.444
hence, the term inflammaging,

647
00:36:37.314 --> 00:36:41.154
that is present in older patients, and this

648
00:36:41.194 --> 00:36:44.594
epithelial cell-specific phenotype of epithelial-mesenchymal

