00:37:50.264 --> 00:37:52.044
through a couple of the tools that we've developed.

668
00:37:52.104 --> 00:37:56.054
First of all, in order to study aging, we are

669
00:37:56.244 --> 00:37:59.744
essentially just using younger and aged

