00:39:46.064 --> 00:39:49.764
enter them into any study, any question we want to ask,

701
00:39:50.404 --> 00:39:53.224
and then get a very quick answer by a simple

702
00:39:53.264 --> 00:39:56.164
PCR-based readout and

703
00:39:56.184 --> 00:39:58.964
quantification of those barcodes.

704
00:40:00.044 --> 00:40:03.804
So just an example. We published a number of years ago now,

705
00:40:04.384 --> 00:40:08.044
but these barcodes have inter- and intra-clonal

