00:40:19.584 --> 00:40:23.384
of various markers. Importantly, the barcoded pooled

710
00:40:23.484 --> 00:40:27.284
population has similar growth kinetics to the original parental

711
00:40:27.364 --> 00:40:29.824
cell line. We haven't messed it up in any way.

712
00:40:30.264 --> 00:40:34.244
And a card-carrying breast pathologist, human breast pathologist,

713
00:40:34.684 --> 00:40:38.544
looking at these tumors, classified them blindly, she didn't

