00:40:38.614 --> 00:40:41.964
know whether we were studying mouse or human, as Grade 3

715
00:40:42.344 --> 00:40:45.244
adenocarcinoma with stromal and intratumoral TILs.

716
00:40:45.944 --> 00:40:48.044
So we're convinced we have a pretty nice model.

717
00:40:48.684 --> 00:40:52.604
So the question then that was posed primarily by Milos

