00:41:09.524 --> 00:41:12.564
cancer progression and response to therapy?

724
00:41:13.344 --> 00:41:16.564
And that's important when we think about immune fitness and immune aging.

725
00:41:16.824 --> 00:41:20.484
We've seen a variation of this curve many, many

726
00:41:20.584 --> 00:41:24.204
times that we know over our lifespan that the risk

