1173
01:07:02.754 --> 01:07:05.654
or T cell low in terms of infiltration into the tumors.

1174
01:07:06.134 --> 01:07:09.074
Now, this is their prototypic T cell low cold clone,

1175
01:07:09.154 --> 01:07:12.754
KPCY-C5. You can see here again, in older

1176
01:07:12.814 --> 01:07:16.750
animals, the tumors grow faster in the pancreata.But even

1177
01:07:16.810 --> 01:07:20.410
again, what was supposed to be a cold model in young mice as it was developed,

1178
01:07:20.990 --> 01:07:24.810
here I can show you that total immune cell infiltration is around the same here

1179
01:07:24.970 --> 01:07:28.880
by flow cytometry, but there's a big reduction in the infiltration

1180
01:07:28.910 --> 01:07:32.790
of CD8 T cells, CD4 T cells, and intratumoral dendritic

1181
01:07:32.850 --> 01:07:36.710
cells, kind of hinting that the age microenvironment is a key determinant

