1197
01:08:29.771 --> 01:08:33.471
with, or the ones that were there were just ineffective at controlling tumor growth

1198
01:08:33.610 --> 01:08:34.170
in this model.

1199
01:08:35.570 --> 01:08:37.510
And it got us thinking, well, what's going on?

1200
01:08:37.590 --> 01:08:41.450
We know there's changes in the microenvironment, in the host, and we took a look at

1201
01:08:41.471 --> 01:08:45.311
what's going on in patients. So we looked at a publicly

1202
01:08:45.351 --> 01:08:47.590
available data set of circulating cytokines and

1203
01:08:48.630 --> 01:08:52.360
